instructions: Based on the Apocalypse World 1st Edition sheet by Ryan Sigg, Steve K., and Natha. For feature requests or issues please add them to the [issue tracker](https://github.com/AuthorX/Fellowship-for-Roll20/issues). Things that are currently missing are fields for Webs (for Spider expansion), Orc-Made Weapons, and the various Destiny advances (you can select a Destiny, though).
